<remarks>
<para>The <strong><c>BluetoothRemoteGATTCharacteristic.writeValue()</c></strong> method sets a <see cref="BluetoothRemoteGATTCharacteristic"/> object's <c>value</c> property to the bytes contained in a given <see cref="ArrayBuffer"/>, <see href="https://webbluetoothcg.github.io/web-bluetooth/#writecharacteristicvalue">writes the characteristic value with optional response</see>, and returns the resulting <see cref="Promise"/>.</para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/BluetoothRemoteGATTCharacteristic/writeValue"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
